Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hidden Power:\N The Purpose of the God Cards"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling all Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now be taking a 20 minute break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please report to the Bing Machine after that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will then hold the lottery for the second round of the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just 20 minutes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s room?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right here, but what do you want with my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! You're in there, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't bother my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Kaiba! Open up!\N -Stop it, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Oi!\N -Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaib-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's the deadbeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even {\i1}you{\i0} should know how important the time before a battle is for a Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now isn't the time to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to land the Battle Ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} still hasn't woken up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's bleeding a heck of a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was already pushing himself too much leaving the hospital and coming on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you expect me to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please land the blimp and take him to a hospital so he can be looked at!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the reason may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he is responsible for Dueling with those injuries in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People's lives are more important than these Duels!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should listen to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have even the {\i1}slightest{\i0} bit of human blood flowing in you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot land this ship now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send the medical staff to room number six.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a team of doctors on board the Battle Ship with training better than any local hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in good hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}! That was well said back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you told Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}, "People's lives are more important than these Duels!",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I literally felt my heart {\i1}move{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sooo moved~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we've got no choice but to leave Bakura with Kaiba's supposed skilled medical team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm gonna go search for Bakura's missing Millennium Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we'll give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've got to focus on the coming Duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duelists have a lot on their minds right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing anything but cheering you guys on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us handle the tedious stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, shall we go look together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi, come with {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Ring's hard to spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be too hard on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go search together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they {\i1}can{\i0} be useful sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. But don't you think Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s acting a bit weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not up here anywhere.\N Let's go search some place else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I've got the chance,\N I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been bugging me ever\N since we met in Domino City.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What has?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that\N you are getting too close to Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what you could be thinking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}, what exactly {\i1}are{\i0} you to Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you her {\i1}lover{\i0} or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd understand if her brother Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} was upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think that\N you have the right to question me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm free to do whatever I {\i1}like{\i0} with Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of dragging me all the way out here and tossing around uncanny accusations,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you play this fair and square by confessing to Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0} {\i1}yourself{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, even if you do, I think it's {\i1}clear{\i0} who the winner of this competition is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asshole! You {\i1}askin'{\i0} for a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna {\i1}try{\i0} it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to {\i1}kill{\i0} me, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Hold on tightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody there?!\N Anybody up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Hey! Somebody please help us!\N -Anyone there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit... No one's gonna be up there {\i1}now{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...! \NMy hands just went numb...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\N You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it..!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't... take it anymore...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! We owe you our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone... The man cloaked in white who saved us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man cloaked in white?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Shadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on my investigation in the Duelist Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that the seal on the Millennium Puzzle had been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you have learned the identity of the other "you" residing within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, my other self is the soul of a Pharaoh sealed within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct, vessel to the Pharaoh's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always appearing to me in incredible ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a guardian of the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And currently, all seven items are gathered aboard this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adding to that, the God Cards are here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the requirements needed to open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Pharaoh's memories are gathered aboard this Battle Ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But listen carefully, vessel holding the Pharaoh's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the Millennium Items and the God Cards
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may only be used by those chosen to wield them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one who is not chosen tries to use them, they shall suffer God's wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God's... wrath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once in the past, Pegasus traveled to Egypt in the hopes of bringing back his dead lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon after, he discovered palettes containing the images of strange monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being tempted by those palettes,\N Pegasus returned to Egypt several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sought out the stones depicting the truth behind the Pharaoh and his Royal Priests.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Monsters game revived soon after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of Duel Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Monsters game revived soon after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of Duel Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus studied the palettes for years
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and learned of the existence of three "God Cards"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He then finally decided to locate these God Cards himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why can't we find the God Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am most certain that the God Cards exist! They are not a myth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why I can't I find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Duel Monsters shall not be complete until I create the God Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are... Shadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The three God Cards have been sealed by the Tomb Guardians and their Power of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You won't find them\N no matter how hard you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But with my power,\N I can show you them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really? Please!\N Show me those palettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's hard to believe there's a village down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! It seems somebody is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can no longer see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are about to open a door to history here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, three God Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross over 3,000 years of time and revive once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jesus! At long last I've finally found the three God Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, great! At long last I can finally complete my Duel Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus then went back to America
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to design the images he found in the pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I had no idea of the terror to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That moment I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not those chosen by the Millennium Items
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could control the gods as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? all the people involved in the God Card expedition have all died?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jesus! At long last I've finally found the three God Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, great! At long last I can finally complete my Duel-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even for Ancient Egyptian language, these words are something special!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can't decipher their meaning, the cards can't be completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And others involved grew delusional and had panic attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think it's all just a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must insist that you stop the production of the God Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The development of Duel Monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is our company's opportunity to become a big hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We shall create a new page in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you suggesting we waste such an opportunity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you're implying this is "God's wrath"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, I will take the full brunt of that wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it be the power of the gods or the power of darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can control both with no trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now I'm a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen to me, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duel Monsters is not just a mere game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It holds the power to destroy the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if it {\b0}is{\b1} a Dark Game, I have to bring Duel Monsters to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If my soul is to be devoured by the devil himself, then so be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You cannot control all three cards at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless you are to seal them away in Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}NO~!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That overwhelming heat, power and pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no way that was a mere illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Pegasus had completed the three God Cards himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he himself had experienced the extremely horrible power of the cards firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He decided to seal the cards away himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that you have come to return these cards to their rightful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus J. Crawford.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Pegasus received a visit from that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And by that, you mean Ishizu-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:19:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Vessel of the great Pharaoh's spirit, please deliver my words to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me directly, Shadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am most sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All seven items are present aboard this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to do now is win the Duels and open the gate with your own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All participants of the tournament, please report to the main lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'll gather all three cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a man cloaked in white!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was really scary, eh Otogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really didn't see him myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, stop trying to scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd believe that story anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there really could be a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, not you too Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! You freakin' scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the story, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here, dear sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A horrible fate awaits Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Dueling in order to prevent that horrible fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(139,139)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one chosen to be Jounouchi's opponent in the second match
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the one who brainwashed us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and forced a fight between friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't ever forgive {\i1}him{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! Pay him back tenfold in the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to the energetic and impatient Jounouchi, Malik is calm and gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant temple appeared on Malik's field!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jounouchi VS the Trap Deck"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
